item.title: Project Post 1
item.description: Do you remember that episode of The Wonder Years where Kevin Arnold’s Dad was finally convinced to sell the old family station wagon? The family loved the allure of trading up to a newer vehicle, but once they began to wash that wagon one last time nostalgia feels slapped at their heartstrings. It’s kind of like that the first time you sell your old guitar. You remember your first riffs. Your first band.
